'''Emily''' is one of [[Leo Hunt|Leo's]] babysitters.

==History==
When Teddy went into labor at Owen's house with only Amelia and Leo there, Amelia called Emily's mom, who sent her over to babysit Leo so Amelia could take Teddy to the hospital. When she saw Amelia looking at her watch and Teddy panting on the couch, she asked what was going on.
